for inviting me here
today to speak.

00:07:07.260 --> 00:07:10.080
It's a great pleasure
to be here.

00:07:10.080 --> 00:07:12.280
And I also wanted to
acknowledge how much of a part

00:07:12.280 --> 00:07:16.050
